14:["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-10","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4","children":"Kalkulyatordan qanday foydalanish"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-sm sm:prose-base max-w-none text-muted-foreground space-y-4","children":[["$","div","0",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Kalkulyator qanday ishlaydi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"O'zbekistonda qo'shilgan qiymat solig'i (QQS) stavkasi 12% — MDHdagi eng past stavkalardan biri. QQS tovarlar va xizmatlar narxiga kiritilgan bilvosita soliq bo'lib, amalda yakuniy iste'molchi tomonidan to'lanadi. QQSni hisoblash va to'lash majburiyati ketma-ket 12 oy davomida umumiy aylanmasi 60 000 "}],["$","$La","1",{"href":"/uz/calculator/bhm","localeCookie":"$3:props:children:props:children:props:children:0:props:localeCookie","className":"text-emerald-700 dark:text-emerald-400 hover:underline underline-offset-2 decoration-emerald-500/40 font-medium","children":"BHK"}],["$","$1","2",{"children":" (2025-yil avgust holatiga ko'ra 24 720 000 000 so'm) chegarasidan oshgan yuridik shaxslar va yakka tartibdagi tadbirkorlarga yuklatiladi."}]]}]]}],["$","div","1",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Hisoblash formulasi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"QQS kalkulyatori ikkita asosiy hisoblashni bajaradi. Summadan QQSni ajratish: QQS bilan narx ma'lum bo'lsa, QQS summasi = QQS bilan narx × 12 / 112, QQSsiz narx = QQS bilan narx × 100 / 112. Summaga QQS hisoblash: QQSsiz narx ma'lum bo'lsa, QQS = QQSsiz narx × 12 / 100, QQS bilan narx = QQSsiz narx × 112 / 100. Masalan, tovar QQS bilan 1 000 000 so'm tursa, QQS summasi = 107 143 so'm, QQSsiz narx = 892 857 so'm."}]]}]]}],["$","div","2",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Hisoblash misoli"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"QQS bo'yicha hisobot davri tushum hajmiga bog'liq: yirik to'lovchilar (100 mlrd so'mdan ortiq aylanma) har oy, qolganlari har chorakda hisobot beradi. Deklaratsiya my.soliq.uz tizimi orqali hisobot davridan keyingi oyning 20-sanasigacha topshiriladi. Tovarlar eksporti va bir qator xalqaro xizmatlarga nol (0%) QQS stavkasi qo'llaniladi. QQSdan ozod: ta'lim va tibbiy xizmatlar, moliyaviy xizmatlar, turar-joy ijarasi."}]]}]]}],["$","div","3",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Nimalarni hisobga olish kerak"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Hisob-kitob (kirish QQS) mexanizmi hisoblangan QQSdan tadbirkorlik faoliyati uchun tovar va xizmatlar sotib olishda yetkazib beruvchilarga to'langan soliq summasini chegirib tashlash imkonini beradi. To'lanadigan QQS = Chiqish QQS − Kirish QQS. Elektron hisob-fakturalar faktura.soliq.uz tizimi orqali rasmiylashtiriladi va kirish QQSni hisobga olish uchun majburiy shartdir."}]]}]]}],["$","div","4",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Foydali maslahatlar"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"2026-yildan boshlab YaTT sifatida ro'yxatdan o'tmagan o'z-o'zini band qilgan shaxslar aylanmadan 1% stavkada soliq to'laydilar — ular aylanma hajmidan qat'i nazar QQS to'lovchilari hisoblanmaydi. Soddalashtilgan tizimda aylanmasi 1 mlrd so'mgacha YaTTlar uchun aylanma solig'i stavkasi 1% (2026-yildan), aylanmasi 1 mlrd dan ortiq bo'lganda esa 4% bo'lib, ularning aylanmasi chegaradan oshmasa QQS to'lamaydilar."}]]}]]}]]}],"$L1a","$L1b","$L1c"]}]
